[
    {
        "content": "<p>I'm new to systems programming and I have some issue with setting up my machine for kernel development using C + Rust.</p>\n<p>I want to understand how to make kernel module, which is written in C, to recognize my rust code. Do I need to specify path to a <code>kernel</code> in Cargo.toml? Do I need to use <a href=\"http://build.rs\">build.rs</a>? </p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/T_8JwztfJBZf2kds5VjOz6XC/Screenshot-2024-08-06-at-3.29.29PM.png\">Screenshot-2024-08-06-at-3.29.29PM.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/35136/T_8JwztfJBZf2kds5VjOz6XC/Screenshot-2024-08-06-at-3.29.29PM.png\" title=\"Screenshot-2024-08-06-at-3.29.29PM.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"3004x1120\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/35136/T_8JwztfJBZf2kds5VjOz6XC/Screenshot-2024-08-06-at-3.29.29PM.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
        "id": 456798189,
        "sender_full_name": "Nikolai Shv",
        "timestamp": 1722933302
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>the Rust code in the kernel is compiled without <code>cargo</code>, so there is no <code>Cargo.toml</code>. You can run <code>make LLVM=1 rust-analyzer</code> to create a <code>rust-project.json</code>.</p>",
        "id": 456799274,
        "sender_full_name": "Benno Lossin",
        "timestamp": 1722933645
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Could you share some more details what you are looking for? Which kernel (source branch &amp; version) do you use?  Is  <code>make LLVM=1 rustavailable</code> happy? Are you able to build the Rust code in the kernel (<code>CONFIG_RUST</code>)? Are you able to build the Rust samples (<code>CONFIG_SAMPLES_RUST</code>)?  Are you able to run these Rust samples? Are you able to build and run a simple self written Rust module? Are you able to build and run your own Rust code?</p>",
        "id": 456823435,
        "sender_full_name": "Dirk Behme",
        "timestamp": 1722941886
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Out.20of.20tree.20module.20-.20Rust.20.2B.20C.20code/near/463179446\">https://rust-for-linux.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Out.20of.20tree.20module.20-.20Rust.20.2B.20C.20code/near/463179446</a></p>",
