        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"411477\">Miguel Ojeda</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/Having.20hard.20times.20.28C.20.2B.20Rust.20in.20kernel.29/near/464020416\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Would you mind pasting the output as text here, rather than taking screenshots? Images cannot be searched for by others, and some people do not render images by default. Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Bash\"><pre><span></span><code>root@ubuntu2404arm:~/rust-out-of-tree-module#<span class=\"w\"> </span>make<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">KDIR</span><span class=\"o\">=</span>/root/rust-for-linux/\nmake<span class=\"w\"> </span>-C<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-for-linux/<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nv\">M</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"nv\">$PWD</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>Entering<span class=\"w\"> </span>directory<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">'/root/rust-for-linux'</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>RUSTC<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>M<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.o\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0425<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>cannot<span class=\"w\"> </span>find<span class=\"w\"> </span>value<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:24:26\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">24</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">72</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                          </span>^^^^^^^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0425<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>cannot<span class=\"w\"> </span>find<span class=\"w\"> </span>value<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:25:27\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">25</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">108</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                           </span>^^^^^^^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0425<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>cannot<span class=\"w\"> </span>find<span class=\"w\"> </span>value<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:26:27\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">26</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                           </span>^^^^^^^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>not<span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>this<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0599<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>no<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>named<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>push<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>struct<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>kernel::prelude::Vec&lt;_&gt;<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>current<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:24:17\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">24</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">72</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                 </span>^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>help:<span class=\"w\"> </span>there<span class=\"w\"> </span>is<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>with<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>similar<span class=\"w\"> </span>name:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>try_push<span class=\"sb\">`</span>\n\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0599<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>no<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>named<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>push<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>struct<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>kernel::prelude::Vec&lt;_&gt;<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>current<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:25:17\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">25</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">108</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                 </span>^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>help:<span class=\"w\"> </span>there<span class=\"w\"> </span>is<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>with<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>similar<span class=\"w\"> </span>name:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>try_push<span class=\"sb\">`</span>\n\nerror<span class=\"o\">[</span>E0599<span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>no<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>named<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>push<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>found<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>struct<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>kernel::prelude::Vec&lt;_&gt;<span class=\"sb\">`</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>the<span class=\"w\"> </span>current<span class=\"w\"> </span>scope\n<span class=\"w\">  </span>--&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.rs:26:17\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span>\n<span class=\"m\">26</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">         </span>numbers.push<span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"m\">200</span>,<span class=\"w\"> </span>GFP_KERNEL<span class=\"o\">)</span>?<span class=\"p\">;</span>\n<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"p\">|</span><span class=\"w\">                 </span>^^^^<span class=\"w\"> </span>help:<span class=\"w\"> </span>there<span class=\"w\"> </span>is<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>method<span class=\"w\"> </span>with<span class=\"w\"> </span>a<span class=\"w\"> </span>similar<span class=\"w\"> </span>name:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>try_push<span class=\"sb\">`</span>\n\nerror:<span class=\"w\"> </span>aborting<span class=\"w\"> </span>due<span class=\"w\"> </span>to<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">6</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>previous<span class=\"w\"> </span>errors\n\nSome<span class=\"w\"> </span>errors<span class=\"w\"> </span>have<span class=\"w\"> </span>detailed<span class=\"w\"> </span>explanations:<span class=\"w\"> </span>E0425,<span class=\"w\"> </span>E0599.\nFor<span class=\"w\"> </span>more<span class=\"w\"> </span>information<span class=\"w\"> </span>about<span class=\"w\"> </span>an<span class=\"w\"> </span>error,<span class=\"w\"> </span>try<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sb\">`</span>rustc<span class=\"w\"> </span>--explain<span class=\"w\"> </span>E0425<span class=\"sb\">`</span>.\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">3</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>scripts/Makefile.build:294:<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module/rust_out_of_tree.o<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">1</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">2</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>/root/rust-for-linux/Makefile:1919:<span class=\"w\"> </span>/root/rust-out-of-tree-module<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>Makefile:240:<span class=\"w\"> </span>__sub-make<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\nmake<span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"m\">1</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>:<span class=\"w\"> </span>Leaving<span class=\"w\"> </span>directory<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">'/root/rust-for-linux'</span>\nmake:<span class=\"w\"> </span>***<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>Makefile:6:<span class=\"w\"> </span>default<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Error<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2</span>\nroot@ubuntu2404arm:~/rust-out-of-tree-module#\n</code></pre></div>",
